title: #270 - Edmund Husserl Pt. 3: The Original Influencer
itunes:title: #270 - Edmund Husserl Pt. 3: The Original Influencer
description: Now that we know who Husserl was and what he did, it's time to look at who came after him. The man's influence on the world of philosophy is perhaps more impressive than anything he actual wrote in his lifetime, but many of the thinkers who came after him would not shy away from criticizing the old man. Connor and Dan peruse the philosophical burn book on this week's episode.
